first_para: Natalie Louise Bennett (born 10 February 1966) is an Australian-born British politician and journalist. She was elected to her position as the leader of the Green Party of England and Wales on 3 September 2012.

full.extract: Natalie Louise Bennett (born 10 February 1966) is an Australian-born British politician and journalist. She was elected to her position as the leader of the Green Party of England and Wales on 3 September 2012.
